PARLIAMENT The ad hoc committee probing the fitness of the SABC board has finalised its report and adopted it, Parliament said on Friday.The report will be published before it is tabled in the National Assembly on Tuesday next week.WATCH: #SABCInquiry committee receives submissions I am confident that the committee has done due diligence to its mandate and believe that the National Assembly will agree with us. I would like to express my appreciation to the team spirit displayed by members of the committee across party lines, as well as the support staff. We would also like to thank the media and the public for their patience and support, said Vincent Smith, committee chairperson.eNCA